theorem Topology.closureInterior_inter_interiorClosure_eq_interiorClosure
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] (A : Set X) :
    closure (interior A) ∩ interior (closure A) = interior (closure A) := by
  ext x
  constructor
  · intro hx; exact hx.2
  · intro hx
    have h₁ : x ∈ closure (interior A) :=
      (Topology.interiorClosure_subset_closureInterior (A := A)) hx
    exact ⟨h₁, hx⟩

theorem Topology.interiorClosure_subset_closureInterior
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    interior (closure A) ⊆ closure (interior (closure A)) := by
  intro x hx
  exact Set.subset_closure hx
